==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*ἔσχατος / eschatos / es'-khat-os
*A superlative probably from G2192 (in the sense of contiguity); farthest, final (of place or time): 

===Noun===
'''ἔσχατος'''

# ends of, [[last]], latter end, lowest, [[uttermost]].

